{"tid":1863073,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獨家突發 「世界夢號」現場","createTime":"2020-02-05T03:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T05:42:47.000Z","uid":120308,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e43e15b6e5c0cd3e8f17fc02971d3d9558dac910","tid":1863073,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:34:49.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】獨家突發 「世界夢號」現場<br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫症持續爆發，各國陸續對疫區或國家進行封關。<br />\n<br />\n「世界夢號」郵輪曾於一月十九日從廣州南沙出發，前住越南，共有乘客4482人，及1814名船員，並於本週一（3日）確認其中三名乘客確診感染。<br />\n<br />\n其後該世界夢號於二月二日從香港出發前往台灣高雄，原定計劃於本日（4日）泊岸高雄港，現已被台灣當局禁止入境。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者現於船上，將繼續更新現場情況<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/404NewsMedia/videos/3112612738758344/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F404NewsMedia%2Fvideos%2F3112612738758344%2F&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=447e199d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/404NewsMedia/videos/3112612738758344/</a>"},{"pid":"ac60f9f5a78fb76a646c41179ef97d648b05a20b","tid":1863073,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:35:57.000Z","msg":"玩命記者[adore]"},{"pid":"fe8e758f85537074e39e64fe6cbf2116ccbeb2dd","tid":1863073,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39450709f297531b213ce2ffdd7a815daa8112c3","tid":1863073,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9924bfdec8f806c2e95ffac2a72dcb6f340e97","tid":1863073,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7efed38bcefd40ee56677de0ac4f0bb8cd0c686","tid":1863073,"uid":254684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"用船傳播了 <br />\n好似玩緊plague Inc"},{"pid":"3108477efb47b7088d383ac22fba249a08e6e162","tid":1863073,"uid":140538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"#啟德 #讀者報料 <br />\n<br />\n1005 啟德郵輪碼頭鑽石公主號落船之旅客將會乘坐以下車牌旅巴到地鐵站<br />\n<br />\nUK6169 UK5526 VW2038 UX7616<br />\nUl1704 UL8816 UM1021 SU1641 UG5436<br />\nVU2980 UB175 PE4202 UH2707<br />\n<br />\n以下城巴巴士車牌亦將會接戴乘客<br />\n<br />\nTM2953 TM2971<br />\n<br />\n===============================<br />\n#延伸新聞<br />\n<br />\n#rthk<br />\n<br />\n日本當局證實，早前香港確診男子曾經乘坐的郵輪「鑽石公主號」，有10人確診感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的郵輪停泊在橫濱港口，現場附近有多架救護車和消防車停泊，厚生勞動省派出幾十人登船，為船上大約3700人進行大規模檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n郵輪上個月20日由橫濱啟程，曾經停靠鹿兒島，25日抵達香港，之後駛往越南及台灣，上星期六在沖繩那霸停靠時，日本當局已經派人檢疫過一次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506704-20200205.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506704-20200205.htm&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=74b529bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506704-20200205.htm&h=edcd49b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506704-20200205.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b81c7d903b9b60ef506caa7d50f5a9e179d815fd","tid":1863073,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49627319a1ffae70c6d6e9499745afc82dd321e","tid":1863073,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7efed38bcefd40ee56677de0ac4f0bb8cd0c686","tid":1863073,"uid":254684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"用船傳播了 <br />\n好似玩緊plague Inc"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:40:26.000Z","